1
00:00:44,830 --> 00:00:45,630
Your Majesty.

2
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:48,360
Since ancient times,

3
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:50,800
women of the harem are forbidden to meddle in politics.

4
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:53,930
Not only did the evil Consort Qu poison Consort Li,

5
00:00:53,930 --> 00:00:56,860
she now dares to arrogantly hold court from behind the screen.

6
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:58,530
This is a woman usurping power,

7
00:00:58,530 --> 00:01:00,330
an omen of the nation's downfall!

8
00:01:00,330 --> 00:01:01,330
Your Majesty,

9
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:05,730
I, along with thirty-eight officials from the Six Ministries,

10
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,430
risk our lives to beseech you

11
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:09,100
to execute this evil consort

12
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,900
and restore order to the court.

13
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,100
Execute the evil consort!

14
00:01:13,100 --> 00:01:14,900
Restore order to the court!

15
00:01:24,300 --> 00:01:26,460
Lord Zhao, you call me an evil consort.

16
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,860
Open your dog eyes and look closely.

17
00:01:33,860 --> 00:01:34,860
What is this?

18
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,800
Li Huai, Vice Minister of Works.

19
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,360
In the third year of Zhaoning,

20
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,759
he embezzled 300,000 taels of official silver

21
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:41,430
meant for riverbank construction

22
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:44,830
and sent it to the Yu army camp at the border as military funds.

23
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,560
Save me, Your Majesty!

24
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,000
I am innocent!

25
00:01:50,460 --> 00:01:52,400
Wang Xian, Deputy Minister of the Court of Stud.

26
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:54,430
Secretly deployed 2,000 warhorses

27
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:55,960
and transported them to enemy generals at the border.

28
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:56,490
Kill him.

29
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,700
Sun Zhao, Supervising Secretary of the Ministry of Personnel.

30
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,330
Colluded with Yu Henian

31
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,160
to forge letters of treason against loyal officials.

32
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:02,960
Kill him.

33
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,430
Lord Zhao.

34
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:16,400
Are you satisfied with

35
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,030
my methods of usurping power?

36
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:18,930
Your Majesty!

37
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:21,230
The evil consort is murdering people in the hall!

38
00:02:21,230 --> 00:02:23,230
The Great Zheng is doomed!

39
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:24,660
Hahaha!

40
00:02:24,930 --> 00:02:26,960
My Great Zheng will not perish.

41
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,630
The remnants of Yu Henian's family

42
00:02:30,829 --> 00:02:33,100
are completely wiped out today.

43
00:02:33,329 --> 00:02:34,360
Jingzhi.

44
00:02:34,930 --> 00:02:37,230
This grand display of fireworks you put on

45
00:02:37,230 --> 00:02:39,160
is very much to my liking.

46
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:43,200
Urgent report from the border!

47
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:45,030
Commander Ying Wujiu led a 100,000-strong army

48
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,460
on a night raid against the Yu army camp,

49
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:49,390
breaking through seven enemy defense lines in a row.

50
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,400
That old thief Yu Henian retreated to Sunset Valley

51
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,660
and detonated the miasma and poisonous fog buried at the bottom of the valley.

52
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,730
To cover the retreat of the main army,

53
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,600
the Commander personally brought up the rear,

54
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:59,160
sealing himself in the deepest part of the poisonous valley.

55
00:02:59,160 --> 00:02:59,930
The Commander's

56
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:01,360
fate is unknown.

57
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,360
Jingzhi.

58
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,460
Why aren't you smiling anymore?

59
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:05,200
Hearing that your loyal eunuch dog

60
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,630
is about to die in the poisonous valley,

61
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,160
does a sharp blade like you

62
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,560
feel pain too?

63
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,400
Hold on.

64
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,000
I must not panic.

65
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:13,760
If I flinch even a little,

66
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:15,230
he will immediately issue

67
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:17,030
a secret edict to slaughter Ying Wujiu.

68
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,130
Pain.

69
00:03:18,130 --> 00:03:19,360
I do feel pain.

70
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,800
What pains me is that

71
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,960
the blood feud of the 134 members of the Qu family

72
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,290
was about to be avenged.

73
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,460
Yet this useless servant

74
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:27,660
couldn't even bring back Yu Henian's head.

75
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:29,390
If he really dies in the miasma,

76
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,460
does Your Majesty want me to go to the border myself

77
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:33,060
to chop off that old dog Yu's head?

78
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:34,260
Good.

79
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,260
Very good.

80
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,100
As long as he's not in your heart,

81
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:40,230
I don't care if he's chopped to pieces.

82
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,960
Jingzhi.

83
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:45,230
That's my Imperial Noble Consort.

84
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:53,130
I cannot die here.

85
00:03:54,329 --> 00:03:57,600
Jingzhi is still waiting for me in that man-eating cage.

86
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,630
Yu Henian.

87
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:13,400
Ying Wujiu.

88
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,960
You think you've won?

89
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:16,230
The Northern Di cavalry

90
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:18,399
will trample through Anding Gate tonight.

91
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,500
You can't protect that demon consort.

92
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:22,300
You will all be buried with me.

93
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,400
To kill me, that madman Helan Ci

94
00:04:25,030 --> 00:04:27,260
must have transferred the city defense forces.

95
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:28,630
Jingzhi is in danger.

96
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,460
Listen to my command.

97
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,600
At all costs,

98
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,030
fight your way out of the Poison Valley

99
00:04:35,030 --> 00:04:37,000
and rush to the capital tonight.

100
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,830
Jingzhi.

101
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:48,430
Ying Wujiu is going to win.

102
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,530
If he wins,

103
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:54,330
Yu Henian's family will be destroyed.

104
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:59,260
But suddenly, I don't want him to come back.

105
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:00,760
Jingzhi,

106
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:02,860
if he were on his way back to the court

107
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:04,790
and unfortunately assassinated,

108
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:06,300
would you be sad?

109
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,600
When the birds are gone,

110
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,130
the good bow is hidden away.

111
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:10,900
He never intended to let Ying Wujiu

112
00:05:10,900 --> 00:05:12,100
enter the city alive.

113
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:18,860
The so-called remnants of Yu Henian's family

114
00:05:19,030 --> 00:05:21,660
are definitely the Royal Guards deployed by himself.
